videos.description: Thomas Dziagwa of Oklahoma State hits a pair of 3-pointers around a deep Eric Paschall trey early in the game.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State, Villanova exchange flurry of 3s

videos.description: Cameron McGriff gets Dick Vitale excited with his follow-up slam.
videos.headline: McGriff punches home dunk

videos.description: Dick Vitale recaps Eric Paschall's 20-point first half in which he went 6-7 on 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Paschall drops 20 in big first half

videos.description: Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree collects the dish from Collin Gillespie and slams to stem Oklahoma State's second-half run.
videos.headline: Villanova ices game with dish-and-dunk
